<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>青蛙 — QLand 笑話</title>
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0b0a10;
    --text:#e4d8c4;
    --text-dim:#a89a82;
    --accent:#d4a574;
    --border:#2a2420;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{
    background:var(--bg);
    color:var(--text);
    font-family:"Noto Serif TC","Songti TC","PMingLiU",serif;
    line-height:1.9;
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
  }
  .site-header{
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f5ecda 0%,#eadcbe 100%);
    border-bottom:1px solid #dbcdb0;
    padding:28px 24px;
  }
  .header-inner{
    max-width:960px;
    margin:0 auto;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:18px;
    position:relative;
    padding-top:6px;
  }
  .home-link{
    position:absolute;
    left:0;
    top:8px;
    color:#5a4638;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-size:18px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    transition:opacity .2s;
  }
  .home-link:hover{opacity:.7}
  .title-block{text-align:center}
  .page-title{
    font-size:30px;
    font-weight:800;
    color:#2a1008;
    letter-spacing:6px;
    line-height:1.2;
  }
  .page-subtitle{
    font-size:16px;
    color:#3e2212;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    margin-top:4px;
  }
    .container{padding:26px 18px}
    .chapter-title{font-size:22px}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a class="home-link" href="/QLand/">回首頁</a>
    <div class="title-block">
      <div class="page-title">青蛙</div>
      <div class="page-subtitle">笑話</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<div class="container">
  <div class="chapter-num">笑話</div>
  <h1 class="chapter-title">青蛙</h1>
  <div class="chapter-body">
    <p>有一天，一隻青蛙在路上遇到一隻烏龜。</p>
    <p>青蛙笑烏龜走得慢，烏龜沒理牠，繼續爬。</p>
    <p>青蛙又叫：「你這麼慢，乾脆回家睡覺好了！」</p>
    <p>烏龜終於抬起頭，平靜地說：「我慢，可是我沒有停在原地啊。」</p>
    <p>青蛙瞬間尷尬。</p>
    <p>從那天起，青蛙再也不笑烏龜慢了。</p>
    <p>──</p>
    <p>誰說快，就一定贏？</p>
  </div>
  <div class="chapter-nav">
    <a class="disabled">← 上一章</a>
    <a class="disabled">下一章 →</a>
  </div>
</div>
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-text">QLand — 繁體中文小說平台</div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
